== Births == * {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1666]] {{ill|June 18|ja|6月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Mamabe Senbō|ja|間部詮房|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the first lord of the Murakami Domain in Echigo (died [[1720]]). * {{ill|Enkyō|ja|延享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1744]] {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Mizuno Tadayoshi|ja|水野忠鼎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the second lord of the Karatsu Domain (died [[1818]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1575]] {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Torii Qiyūemon|ja|鳥居強右衛門|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a samurai (born [[1540]]). * [[Genna]] 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1623]] {{ill|June 13|ja|6月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hon'inbō Sansa|ja|本因坊算砂|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, an accomplished go player and the first head of the Hon'inbō house (born [[1559]]). * [[Bunka]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1807]] {{ill|June 21|ja|6月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Minagawa Kien|ja|皆川淇園|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (born [[1734]]).
