== Events == * {{ill|Reiki|ja|霊亀|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[716]] {{ill|June 10|ja|6月10日|qq=}}) – The Eastern court relocated 1,799 people of Goguryeo origin to Musashi and established the {{ill|Kōrai-gun|ja|高麗郡|qq=}}. * [[Genki (era)|Genki]] 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1571]] {{ill|June 8|ja|6月8日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|qq=}} attacked the stronghold of the Ise-based {{ill|Chōshū Ikki|ja|長島一向一揆|qq=}} at {{ill|Ganshōji|ja|願証寺|qq=}}, suffering heavy losses led by {{ill|Ujige Naomoto|ja|氏家直元|qq=}}. * [[Kansei]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1792]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=}}) – The publication of Hayashikodaira's work, 【Kaikoku Heidan】, was banned; its author, Hayashikodaira, was subsequently imprisoned. * [[Keiō]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1868]] {{ill|March 26|ja|3月26日|qq=}}) – The British Minister of Foreign Affairs, reported as part of the 【Chūgoku Shinbun】 (later published as a special extra) covering the events of the restoration.
== Births == * {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1666]] {{ill|June 18|ja|6月18日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Mamabe Senbō|ja|間部詮房|qq=}}, the first lord of the Murakami Domain in Echigo (died [[1720]]). * {{ill|Enkyō|ja|延享|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1744]] {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Mizuno Tadayoshi|ja|水野忠鼎|qq=}}, the second lord of the Karatsu Domain (died [[1818]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1575]] {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Torii Qiyūemon|ja|鳥居強右衛門|qq=}}, a samurai (born [[1540]]). * [[Genna]] 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1623]] {{ill|June 13|ja|6月13日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hon'inbō Sansa|ja|本因坊算砂|qq=}}, an accomplished go player and the first head of the Hon'inbō house (born [[1559]]). * [[Bunka]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1807]] {{ill|June 21|ja|6月21日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Minagawa Kien|ja|皆川淇園|qq=}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=}}) (born [[1734]]).
