{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月十六|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 16일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 16''' is the 16th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Reiki|ja|霊亀|qq=|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[716]] {{ill|June 10|ja|6月10日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The Eastern court relocated 1,799 people of Goguryeo origin to Musashi and established the {{ill|Kōrai-gun|ja|高麗郡|qq=|12=draft}}. * [[Genki (era)|Genki]] 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1571]] {{ill|June 8|ja|6月8日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|qq=|12=draft}} attacked the stronghold of the Ise-based {{ill|Chōshū Ikki|ja|長島一向一揆|qq=|12=draft}} at {{ill|Ganshōji|ja|願証寺|qq=|12=draft}}, suffering heavy losses led by {{ill|Ujige Naomoto|ja|氏家直元|qq=|12=draft}}. * [[Kansei]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1792]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The publication of Hayashikodaira's work, 【Kaikoku Heidan】, was banned; its author, Hayashikodaira, was subsequently imprisoned. * [[Keiō]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1868]] {{ill|March 26|ja|3月26日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The British Minister of Foreign Affairs, reported as part of the 【Chūgoku Shinbun】 (later published as a special extra) covering the events of the restoration.
== Births == * {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|qq=|12=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1666]] {{ill|June 18|ja|6月18日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Mamabe Senbō|ja|間部詮房|qq=|12=draft}}, the first lord of the Murakami Domain in Echigo (died [[1720]]). * {{ill|Enkyō|ja|延享|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1744]] {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Mizuno Tadayoshi|ja|水野忠鼎|qq=|12=draft}}, the second lord of the Karatsu Domain (died [[1818]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1575]] {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Torii Qiyūemon|ja|鳥居強右衛門|qq=|12=draft}}, a samurai (born [[1540]]). * [[Genna]] 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1623]] {{ill|June 13|ja|6月13日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hon'inbō Sansa|ja|本因坊算砂|qq=|12=draft}}, an accomplished go player and the first head of the Hon'inbō house (born [[1559]]). * [[Bunka]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1807]] {{ill|June 21|ja|6月21日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Minagawa Kien|ja|皆川淇園|qq=|12=draft}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=|12=draft}}) (born [[1734]]).
