== Births == * [[:en:Kanbun (era)|Kanbun]] 6th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1666]] [[:en:June 18|June 18]]) – [[:en:Manabe Akifusa|Mamabe Senbō]], the first lord of the Murakami Domain in Echigo (died [[1720]]). * [[:en:Enkyō (Edo period)|Enkyō]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1744]] [[:en:June 26|June 26]]) – {{ill|Mizuno Tadayoshi|ja|水野忠鼎|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizuno Tadayoshi|qq=}}, the second lord of the Karatsu Domain (died [[1818]]).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[1575]] [[:en:June 24|June 24]]) – [[:en:Torii Suneemon|Torii Qiyūemon]], a samurai (born [[1540]]). * [[Genna]] 9th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1623]] [[:en:June 13|June 13]]) – [[:en:Hon'inbō Sansa|Hon'inbō Sansa]], an accomplished go player and the first head of the Hon'inbō house (born [[1559]]). * [[Bunka]] 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1807]] [[:en:June 21|June 21]]) – {{ill|Minagawa Kien|ja|皆川淇園|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minagawa Kien|qq=}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru|qq=}}) (born [[1734]]).
