== Events == * [[:en:Reiki (era)|Reiki]] 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:716|716]] [[:en:June 10|June 10]]) – The Eastern court relocated 1,799 people of Goguryeo origin to Musashi and established the {{ill|Kōrai-gun|ja|高麗郡|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōrai-gun|qq=}}. * [[Genki (era)|Genki]] 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1571|1571]] [[:en:June 8|June 8]]) – [[:en:Oda Nobunaga|Oda Nobunaga]] attacked the stronghold of the Ise-based [[:en:Sieges of Nagashima|Chōshū Ikki]] at {{ill|Ganshōji|ja|願証寺|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ganshōji|qq=}}, suffering heavy losses led by [[:en:Ujiie Naomoto|Ujige Naomoto]]. * [[Kansei]] 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1792|1792]] [[:en:July 4|July 4]]) – The publication of Hayashikodaira's work, 【Kaikoku Heidan】, was banned; its author, Hayashikodaira, was subsequently imprisoned. * [[Keiō]] 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1868|1868]] [[:en:March 26|March 26]]) – The British Minister of Foreign Affairs, reported as part of the 【Chūgoku Shinbun】 (later published as a special extra) covering the events of the restoration.
